node.text:
Mercedes-AMG goes electric: In addition to the first performance hybrid, electric mobility wins another powerful new star: the all-electric Mercedes-AMG EQS. At the heart of the luxury saloon is the performance-oriented drive concept with two AMG-specific electric motors. The AMG EQS perfectly combines electric intelligence, sportiness and agile driving dynamics. Join the new star at our digital world premiere.

#AMGgoesE #EPERFORMANCE #MercedesAMG #EQS #MercedesEQ #Performanceluxury

node.title: Explore our new all-electric AMG EQS

node.text:
Meet the luxury electric SUV of the future. The Concept Mercedes-Maybach EQS combines the sophisticated luxury of Maybach with the purely electric vehicle architecture from Mercedes-EQ. With futuristic design, emotional integration, and state-of-the-art electric drive technology, the Maybach concept announces a locally emission-free era for the brand.

Join our digital world premiere.

#MercedesMaybach #Maybach #EQS #MercedesEQ #luxury #MBIAA21 #IAA21

In our new episode of AMG Uncovered, Jess explains how important it was to overcome the common stereotypes in order to unlock her true self.
